  "text": "Neuroscientific SNN models vary in complexity and computational/communication demands. The best choice of SNN model depends on the targeted accuracy level and the available execution platform [CITATION_1] . There are three main categories of SNNs: (A) Integrate & Fire models, (B) Izhikevich models, and (C) Conductance(-based) models.",
